name: Fill payload with slot, model, version and serial
set test moduleId
Store DCM220 or DCM224 cal params
Prepare insert statement with a new serial
func:
msg.connectName = 'bb3-ate';  // connect name from settings.js

msg.payload = `
INSERT INTO modules(serial, model, version, added_by, created_at) 
VALUES(
    (
        SELECT 
            LPAD(CAST(CAST(COALESCE(MAX(serial), '000000000000000000000000') AS DECIMAL) + 1 AS TEXT), 24, '0') AS serial
        FROM modules WHERE model= '${flow.get('model')}'
    ), 
    '${flow.get('model')}', 
    '${flow.get('version')}',
    current_user,
    NOW()
) RETURNING *`;

return msg;
